title: Day Light Not So Saving Time ( Godfrey Interview)
itunes:title: Day Light Not So Saving Time ( Godfrey Interview)
description:
Today on the show we had first time guest comedian Godfrey stop by, who has been way over due for an interview. But please note that, we are not responsible for his comments, as he spoke about Chicago Comedy, T.I. Mixup, Steve Harvey, Trump Audiences, Nigerian Culture and so much more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Gary Road Elementary School in Byram for firing the assistant principle for reading a book "I need a New Butt".
